data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.875% VA Loan available! Any buyer can apply, you do not have to be VA eligible. *Seller offering $5,000 towards buyer's closing costs with acceptable offer and terms to seller* Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom beautiful Craftsman-style home. Centrally located, this property offers both comfort and convenience to surrounding schools, parks, and restaurants. The interior features an open concept living space with tile floors and carpet throughout the living room and bedrooms. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and sleek granite countertops, perfect for cooking and hosting gatherings. The primary suite is generously sized and features double vanities in the primary bath, along with a spacious shower. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members and guests. Step into the fenced backyard for outdoor enjoyment and privacy. The location is ideal, with schools, restaurants, and City of Lynn Haven all within close proximity. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this home. All measurements are approximate, buyer to verify any information deemed important.
